Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.96,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(360,360)}Decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I relinquish all ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you... {\alpha&HFF&}take care of Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you... take care of Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stalker-san? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop playing games now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker? {\alpha&HFF&}What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker? What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's suddenly undergone a complete change in attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as I have Ryuk's Death Note, even if I discard Rem's Death Note, I won't forget about Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, as long as I have Ryuk's Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}even if I discard Rem's Death Note, I won't forget about Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, as long as I have Ryuk's Death Note, even if I discard Rem's Death Note, I won't forget about Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Rem... {\alpha&HFF&}it's thanks to you bringing another Death Note into the human world that I've ended up in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Rem... it's thanks to you bringing another Death Note into the human world that I've ended up in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really sure about this, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, {\alpha&HFF&}I never guessed the notebook I gave you would end up discarded in the ground somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I never guessed the notebook I gave you would end up discarded in the ground somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Ryuk... {\alpha&HFF&}for the moment, I've only hidden it in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Ryuk... for the moment, I've only hidden it in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will discard it... {\alpha&HFF&}the very next time the word "discard" escapes my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will discard it... the very next time the word "discard" escapes my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the context in which I say it, when I say that word, I'll mean it in relation to discarding the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san? This is a felony, you know, please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san? {\alpha&HFF&}Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san? Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like this ever since she passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, she really thinks she can feign innocence, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, why don't you just take off my blindfold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san, I really want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san, call Mogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi-san, when you arrested Amane Misa, you said it was on suspicion of being the second Kira, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We covered up her eyes and mouth from behind, and said clearly, so she could hear, "we're arresting you on suspicion of being the second Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't attempt to resist the handcuffs or the blindfold. She seemed pretty resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my autograph and shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! I'll kiss you on the cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been discussing the second Kira for a while already... {\alpha&HFF&}why has she started talking about a stalker now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been discussing the second Kira for a while already... why has she started talking about a stalker now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finally decided to release me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you fell asleep, you were denying everything, and even went as far as saying "kill me", yet, now we have a senseless struggle like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san, you were the one who knocked out and brought Misa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want to do an "Investigation of Amane Misa" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why you're tied up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? {\alpha&HFF&}It's because Misa's an idol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? It's because Misa's an idol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Stalker-san, you're the first to have gone this far for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared... what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! {\alpha&HFF&}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... that's right. I have to go to the bathroom again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom! I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the bathroom only four minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! If I didn't say, I'd have to go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to see Misa wet herself again, won't that be fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... {\alpha&HFF&}a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, {\alpha&HFF&}let's be serious and continue our discussion from before you fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, let's be serious and continue our discussion from before you fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get to know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't I know my own boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, she didn't confess a thing, {\alpha&HFF&}yet now she's openly calling him her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, she didn't confess a thing, yet now she's openly calling him her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn off the video and audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in room 2801 at the K.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.76,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,K is the abbreviated name of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son is coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}it's as I said on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, it's as I said on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... {\alpha&HFF&}might be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... might be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-{\alpha&HFF&}Don't be stupid! What are you saying?! Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid! {\alpha&HFF&}What are you saying?! Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid! What are you saying?! {\alpha&HFF&}Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid! What are you saying?! Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?! {\alpha&HFF&}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no proof that Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you're saying "I might be Kira"... {\alpha&HFF&}it's an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you're saying "I might be Kira"... it's an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you "might be" Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}you {\b1}are{\b0} Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you "might be" Kira, you {\b1}are{\b0} Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, {\alpha&HFF&}if Ryuuzaki is L, it's not an exaggeration to say that he's the best detective in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, if Ryuuzaki is L, {\alpha&HFF&}it's not an exaggeration to say that he's the best detective in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, if Ryuuzaki is L, it's not an exaggeration to say that he's the best detective in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That same L is labeling me as Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}I have to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That same L is labeling me as Kira. I have to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What are you saying?! Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?! {\alpha&HFF&}Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?! Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who the FBI investigator Ray Penber was investigating from the time he came to Japan until he died...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who was in Aoyama on the 22nd of May...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who Amane Misa, the suspected second Kira, immediately made advances on after coming here from Kanto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in L's shoes, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd deduce that I was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in L's shoes, I'd deduce that I was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that subconsciously, I might have become Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}subconsciously, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... subconsciously, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even understand myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm not conscious of it, {\alpha&HFF&}I could be killing people while I sleep or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm not conscious of it, I could be killing people while I sleep or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, there was a period of five days where we set up surveillance cameras in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You slept normally at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having seen that criminals continued to die, despite you having no access to information about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I concluded not that you were innocent; {\alpha&HFF&}merely that, if you were Kira, you would not give yourself away on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I concluded not that you were innocent; merely that, if you were Kira, you would not give yourself away on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you were Kira, you wouldn't give yourself away", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm honest, {\alpha&HFF&}I've sometimes thought that some criminals would be better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm honest, I've sometimes thought that some criminals would be better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think anyone who thinks this way could become Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun! I'm exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often find myself thinking that certain people would be better off dead, {\alpha&HFF&}but that doesn't mean we would really go and kill them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often find myself thinking that certain people would be better off dead, but that doesn't mean we would really go and kill them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, criminals that you had no knowledge of continued to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The surveillance cameras proved this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}No... at the time, we didn't have enough manpower, and only watched his movements inside of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... {\alpha&HFF&}at the time, we didn't have enough manpower, and only watched his movements inside of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... at the time, we didn't have enough manpower, and only watched his movements inside of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we watched him 24/7 over those five days, {\alpha&HFF&}so he may have had a way of killing people when he was out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we watched him 24/7 over those five days, so he may have had a way of killing people when he was out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you predict that things would turn out this way, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}if we detain him like Amane, and criminals continue to die... that would make Yagami Light not Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we detain him like Amane, {\alpha&HFF&}and criminals continue to die... that would make Yagami Light not Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we detain him like Amane, and criminals continue to die... {\alpha&HFF&}that would make Yagami Light not Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we detain him like Amane, and criminals continue to die... that would make Yagami Light not Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I don't like the way this conversation is heading, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll restrain Yagami Light, and imprison him long term.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}imprisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... imprisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to do this, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll start now, by making sure he never goes anywhere I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to do this, we'll start now, by making sure he never goes anywhere I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This is stupid! There's no way my son could be Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is stupid! {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way my son could be Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is stupid! There's no way my son could be Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son would never--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't continue chasing Kira, when deep down, I don't even know whether I'm Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, {\alpha&HFF&}until you have absolutely no doubt about whether I'm innocent or Kira, no matter what happens or what I say, don't let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, until you have absolutely no doubt about whether I'm innocent or Kira, no matter what happens or what I say, don't let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}can you come up with an excuse for Light-kun's absence for your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, can you come up with an excuse for Light-kun's absence for your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}All of a sudden, you can't expect me to--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All of a sudden, you can't expect me to--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I can't understand why my son has to be imprisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stubborn, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only method by which I'll be able to convince myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sealing away my freedom, I'm going to win against the fear that Kira lurks inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:09:51.98,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.83,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fscx91.25\fscy103.75\pos(356,390)}Imprisonment: Day One
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that remains is to discard the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be stuck with no apples to eat again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}I want you to remove me from the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, I want you to remove me from the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one currently imprisoned under suspicion of being Kira is my own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we were discussing his imprisonment, I tried to prevent it due to my own personal feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't let your personal feelings get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}If it turns out that my son is Kira, I don't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If it turns out that my son is Kira, I don't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}it's not unimaginable that you may think to kill your son and then yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... it's not unimaginable that you may think to kill your son and then yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, it's better that you aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like you to imprison me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, I'd like you to imprison me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no idea what I might do, due to feelings for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you might say something like this, {\alpha&HFF&}so I've asked Watari to make the necessary arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you might say something like this, so I've asked Watari to make the necessary arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}though you will be imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, though you will be imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will have your cell phone turned on, now and again as usual, and will continue to communicate with your family and the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun won't be informed of this, {\alpha&HFF&}and if he talks to you, we need him to think that you're still part of this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun won't be informed of this, and if he talks to you, {\alpha&HFF&}we need him to think that you're still part of this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun won't be informed of this, and if he talks to you, we need him to think that you're still part of this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you are imprisoned, {\alpha&HFF&}you will be kept up to date with the investigation at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you are imprisoned, you will be kept up to date with the investigation at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that fine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.24,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fscx98\fscy100\pos(357,392)}Imprisonment: Day Three
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I want to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san, I want to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing you know where I live anyway... fetch me a change of clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting super crazy around here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel really bad for the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any reports of new criminals that were likely to be targeted by Kira yesterday or the day before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they were reported, have they been killed by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been reports of some likely criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}but ever since you were imprisoned, not a single criminal has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been reports of some likely criminals, but ever since you were imprisoned, not a single criminal has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've stopped being killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}looks like they're finally going to decide that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... looks like they're finally going to decide that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to eat an apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that even if I imprisoned Yagami Light, the killings would continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, they've completely stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though he was voluntarily offering to imprison himself, {\alpha&HFF&}but the way this is going, he'll end up as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though he was voluntarily offering to imprison himself, but the way this is going, {\alpha&HFF&}he'll end up as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though he was voluntarily offering to imprison himself, but the way this is going, he'll end up as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the question remains, {\alpha&HFF&}whether or not he was conscious of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the question remains, whether or not he was conscious of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}does he think that pretending to be unaware of it will make it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is Kira, does he think that pretending to be unaware of it will make it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like Yagami Light... {\alpha&HFF&}no, it isn't like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like Yagami Light... no, {\alpha&HFF&}it isn't like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like Yagami Light... no, it isn't like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.04,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fscx105\fscy100\pos(357,392)}Imprisonment: Day Five
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't eat an apple soon--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the only thing to do is to be patient... even if there's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker-san... you won't be able to sell a video of me just sitting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san seems to be in a much worse condition than Light-kun or Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the five days Light-kun has been imprisoned, not a single reported criminal has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this kind of situation, it's harder on the parent than the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, this has pretty much decided that Light-kun is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good or bad news?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...umm, no. {\alpha&HFF&}I think it would be better if you don't think too much about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...umm, no. I think it would be better if you don't think too much about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you're thinking as you sit there, it won't affect the end results.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you rest in a more relaxing environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as a relaxing environment in my current circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most relaxing place for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the result is, when I leave here, it will be with my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.62,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fscx97.5\fscy100\pos(357,391)}Imprisonment: Day Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}it's only been a week, but you look exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, it's only been a week, but you look exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably about time... {\alpha&HFF&}now that I've gotten this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably about time... now that I've gotten this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't say that I look too good at the moment... {\alpha&HFF&}but such meaningless pride... I'll discard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't say that I look too good at the moment... but such meaningless pride... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll discard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't say that I look too good at the moment... but such meaningless pride... I'll discard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I chose to be imprisoned and go through with this, {\alpha&HFF&}but I've just realized, there's no point in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I chose to be imprisoned and go through with this, but I've just realized, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no point in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I chose to be imprisoned and go through with this, but I've just realized, there's no point in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I'm sure whether you're Kira or not, no matter what you say, I won't release you. That was the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something wrong with me that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually believe that it's possible to do what Kira does and not be aware of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not conscious of being Kira, therefore I am not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also believe that Kira cannot be unaware of who they are, {\alpha&HFF&}but if you are Kira, then it all adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also believe that Kira cannot be unaware of who they are, but if you are Kira, then it all adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we imprisoned you, the killings stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Ryuuzaki, there's no way I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine that I've been set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying is all over the place... but why do I sense I'm getting close to the root of the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a waste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}How did it turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How did it turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? This isn't like Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's contradicting himself and isn't being logical at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the murdering of criminals has stopped, there's no way we can release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have realized that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter what anyone says, at this rate, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light will be confirmed as Kira. We can close the case, and everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter what anyone says, at this rate, Yagami Light will be confirmed as Kira. We can close the case, and everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.76,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fscx105\fscy100\pos(357,394)}Imprisonment: Day Fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks' worth of criminals were taken out in one shot yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Kira is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.09,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx266.25\fscy100\pos(412,174)\c&HB8BABC&\3c&H484A4C&}Kira Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! {\alpha&HFF&}Kira is on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Kira is on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira was just resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The judgment of criminals has begun again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}Is this true, Matsuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this true, Matsuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}So my son... I can't say I'm happy that the killings have started again, but this means that the suspicions surrounding my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So my son... {\alpha&HFF&}I can't say I'm happy that the killings have started again, but this means that the suspicions surrounding my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So my son... I can't say I'm happy that the killings have started again, but this means that the suspicions surrounding my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, I know Ryuuzaki won't say he's completely "white"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with "grey" then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he was mainly "black" before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that it's a "grey" that's nearly indistinguishable from "white".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we should tell Light-kun--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Matsuda-san, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Matsuda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No criminals have been judged for over the past two weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just admit that you are Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stupid, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised that you think I'm Kira from the way the investigation has been going, but this is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the zoom or whatever to look closely at my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the eyes of someone who's lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, {\alpha&HFF&}are you sure you don't know who Kira is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, are you sure you don't know who Kira is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa would like to know that herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is a superhero that killed the criminal who murdered Misa's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(568,299)}To be continued
